@startuml level2_safety
!theme plain

title Level 2: Safety Domain Architecture\nPassive Safety Systems

skinparam component {
    BackgroundColor Tomato
    BorderColor DarkRed
    ArrowColor Black
}

package "Safety Domain" {

    component "ACU\n(Airbag Control Unit)" as ACU {
        portin p_crash_sensors
        portin p_seat_sensors
        portout p_airbag_deploy
        portout p_crash_signal

        [Crash Detection Algorithm]
        [Airbag Deployment Control]
        [Pretensioner Control]
        [Crash Data Recording]
    }

    component "ODS\n(Occupant Detection System)" as ODS {
        portin p_seat_pressure
        portin p_weight_sensors
        portout p_occupant_data

        [Occupant Classification]
        [Weight Detection]
        [Airbag Optimization]
    }
}

cloud "CAN-HS #1\n500 kbps" as CAN1

' ACU Messages (OpenDBC)
ACU --> CAN1 : **ACU11**\n• Airbag_Status\n• Crash_Detected\n• Pretensioner_Status\nCycle: 10ms, ASIL-D

ACU --> CAN1 : **ACU_CrashData**\n• Crash_Severity\n• Impact_Direction\n• Deployment_Decision\nCycle: 10ms (Event), ASIL-D

CAN1 --> ACU : **ESP12**\n• Vehicle_Stability\n(for crash prediction)

CAN1 --> ACU : **ABS11**\n• Wheel_Speed\n(for impact detection)

' ODS Messages
ODS --> CAN1 : **ODS13**\n• Occupant_Classification\n• Seat_Occupied_FL/FR/RL/RR\n• Weight_FL/FR/RL/RR\nCycle: 100ms, ASIL-C

CAN1 --> ACU : **ODS13**\n• Occupant_Data\n(for airbag optimization)

component "CGW\n(Central Gateway)" as CGW
CAN1 --> CGW : Route to other networks

CGW --> CAN1 : **BCM_DoorStatus**\n(for crash severity)

note right of ACU
  **ACU Key Functions**
  • Crash detection (frontal, side, rollover)
  • Airbag deployment decision
  • Seatbelt pretensioner control
  • Crash data recording (EDR)
  • Post-crash notification

  **Safety Level**: ASIL-D
  **Cycle Time**: 10ms (critical)
  **Sensors**:
  • Frontal crash sensors (2)
  • Side crash sensors (4)
  • Rollover sensor (1)
  • Seat belt sensors (5)
end note

note right of ODS
  **ODS Key Functions**
  • Occupant classification
    (Adult, Child, Infant seat, Empty)
  • Weight detection
  • Airbag deployment optimization
  • Child seat detection

  **Safety Level**: ASIL-C
  **Cycle Time**: 100ms
  **Sensors**:
  • Seat pressure sensors (4)
  • Weight sensors (4)
end note

note bottom of CAN1
  **Safety CAN Messages**

  Critical Messages (10ms):
  • ACU11: Airbag status, crash detection
  • ACU_CrashData: Deployment decision

  Status Messages (100ms):
  • ODS13: Occupant classification

  **Total Messages**: ~5 messages
  **ASIL Level**: C-D (Highest)
  **Priority**: Maximum (Life-critical)

  **Crash Detection Timeline**:
  0ms: Impact detected
  10ms: Crash severity calculated
  15ms: Deployment decision
  20-30ms: Airbag deployment
end note

@enduml
